OL,5, More living people than dead people    
OL,6, were depicted on statues and sculptures
OL,7, in 2023, according to new data seen by 
OL,8, BBC News.                              
OL,10,FIt is the first time this century that 
OL,11,Fthis has happened and reflects a drive 
OL,12,Fto celebrate more people of colour,    
OL,13,Fsaid Art UK, which compiled the data.  
OL,15,FMore than a third of all monuments     
OL,16,Funveiled last year are of black people.
OL,18,FBut overall, the people depicted in    
OL,19,Fpublic sculpture remain "overwhelmingly
OL,20,Fwhite men", the charity said.          
